e, clicking on the "Your Account" link towards the top of the page and then going into the "Stop &amp; start newsletters" section. Alternatively, you can use the "stop" links found in this monthly reminder email.\r\n\r\nMembers automatically get free preset reminders when they sign up. These reminders are sent on email one week before special dates, holidays and events. They can be stopped at anytime.\r\n\r\nAdverts may be included in email reminders (although a "Pro Sender" upgrade is available to remove these adverts from Reminder emails).\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[/av_one_full]'),
