(3399, 2, '2015-06-12 08:42:12', '2015-06-12 07:42:12', '[av_section min_height='''' min_height_px=''500px'' padding=''default'' shadow=''no-shadow'' bottom_border=''no-border-styling'' id='''' color=''alternate_color'' custom_bg='''' src='''' attachment='''' attachment_size='''' attach=''scroll'' position=''top left'' repeat=''no-repeat'' video='''' video_ratio=''16:9'' overlay_opacity=''0.5'' overlay_color='''' overlay_pattern='''' overlay_custom_pattern='''']\r\n[av_heading heading=''Privacy Policy'' tag=''h1'' style=''blockquote modern-quote modern-centered'' size='''' subheading_active=''subheading_below'' subheading_size=''15'' padding=''10'' color='''' custom_font='''']\r\nView our Privacy Policy\r\n[/av_heading]\r\n[/av_section]\r\n\r\n[av_one_fifth first][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_three_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_textblock size='''' font_color='''' color='''']\r\nWe never send unsolicited emails or text messages.\r\n\r\nWe will never pass on any of your personal details, or sell mailing list data, to third parties.\r\n\r\nWe only disclose information to third parties for goods or service delivery purposes such as\r\n\r\npayment authorisation, for security monitoring or if the ownership of Reemindme.com ever\r\n\r\nchanges.\r\n\r\nWebsite statistics are produced allowing Reemindme.com to record Reemindme.com visitor\r\n\r\nnumbers, number of pages viewed and referral source. These statistics do not record any personal\r\n\r\ndata. This data simply helps us to administer and enhance the site and service.\r\n\r\nA harmless item called a "cookie" is used on the site. This is stored on your computer to allow us\r\n\r\nto keep you logged-in. You can turn cookies off. Please refer to the help section of your browser\r\n\r\nsoftware for instructions on how to do this. If you turn off your cookies, you may not be able to\r\n\r\naccess certain areas on this site that require you to login.\r\n\r\nIf you are a registered website user, you can start or stop newsletter subscriptions at any time by\r\n\r\nlogging-in to the site, clicking on the "Your Account" link towards the top of the page and then\r\n\r\ngoing into the "Stop &amp; start newsletters" section. Alternatively, you can use the "stop" links\r\n\r\nfound in all newsletter emails.\r\n\r\nBy signing up, you give us permission to set-up one reminder email to come to you at the end of\r\n\r\neach month if you have no reminders set-up. If you have one or more reminders set-up, you\r\n\r\nwon''t receive this reminder email. You can start or stop this at any time by logging-in to the site,\r\n\r\nclicking on the "Your Account" link towards the top of the page and then going into the "Stop &amp;\r\n\r\nstart newsletters" section. Alternatively, you can use the "stop" links found in this monthly\r\n\r\nreminder email.\r\n\r\nMembers automatically get free preset reminders when they sign up. These reminders are sent on\r\n\r\nemail one week before special dates, holidays and events. They can be stopped at any time.\r\n\r\nAdverts may be included in email reminders (although a "Pro Sender" upgrade is available to\r\n\r\nremove these adverts from Reminder emails).\r\n\r\nReemindme.com must be used to send reminders only\r\n\r\nYou must never use the Reemindme.com service to send spam and must only send email\r\n\r\nreminders / invites to people who have given you permission to do so.\r\n\r\nYou must only send text message reminders to people who have given you prior permission to\r\n\r\nsend reminder text messages to their mobile phone / s.\r\n\r\nReemindme.com must never be used to send promotional newsletters or promotional text\r\n\r\nmessages to both people who you ''do'' or ''do not'' have permission to contact.\r\n\r\nUsing our service to send spam will lead to your account being shut down without warning and\r\n\r\nmay also lead to legal action being taken against you. You agree that you are legally liable for all\r\n\r\ndamages and costs caused by this and that Reemindme.com is in no way liable for your actions\r\n\r\nor any damages you may cause by sending spam or reminders without permission.\r\n\r\nSigning up confirms that you have read and agree to this.\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[/av_three_fifth][av_one_fifth][/av_one_fifth]', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3390-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-12 08:42:12', '2015-06-12 07:42:12', '', 3390, 'http://reemindme.com/3390-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
