nal newsletters or promotional text messages to both people who you ''do'' or ''do not'' have permission to contact.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style="text-align: left;">\r\n	<li>Using our service to send spam will lead to your account being shut down without warning and may also lead to legal action being taken against you. You agree that you are legally liable for all damages and costs caused by this and that Reemindme.com is in no way liable for your actions or any damages you may cause by sending spam or reminders without permission.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<ul style="text-align: left;">\r\n	<li>Signing up confirms that you have read and agree to this.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[/av_three_fifth][av_one_fifth][/av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_layout_row border='''' min_height=''0'' color=''main_color'' mobile=''av-flex-cells'' id='''']\r\n\r\n[av_cell_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_font_icon icon='''' style=''left'' caption='''' link='''' linktarget='''' size=''40px'' position=''left''][/av_font_icon]\r\n\r\n[/av_cell_one_fifth][av_cell_three_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_font_icon icon='''' style=''left'' caption='''' link='''' linktarget='''' size=''40px'' position=''left''][/av_font_icon]\r\n\r\n[/av_cell_three_fifth][av_cell_one_fifth vertical_align=''top'' padding=''30px'' background_color='''' src='''' background_attachment=''scroll'' background_position=''top left'' background_repeat=''no-repeat'']\r\n\r\n[av_font_icon icon='''' style=''left'' caption='''' link='''' linktarget='''' size=''40px'' position=''left''][/av_font_icon]\r\n\r\n[/av_cell_one_fifth][/av_layout_row]', 'Privacy Policy', '', 'inherit', 'open', 'open', '', '3390-revision-v1', '', '', '2015-06-12 09:00:38', '2015-06-12 08:00:38', '', 3390, 'http://reemindme.com/3390-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
