t contact customer service for refund authorization.</strong>\r\n\r\nIf any text message reminder credits have been used in the time between when you made your purchase, and when we process your refund, up to 50paisa (or the equivalent $ / € amount based on the exchange rate on the day the refund) for each text message reminder sent will be deducted from your refund amount first.\r\n\r\nOur system does not deduct text reminder credits from your account if it failed to send a text reminder. But, if we successfully send a text reminder, text message credits will not be refunded due to a fault with your mobile service provider, you not having a signal, your mobile phone being switched off, you not checking our text reminder network coverage and your network was not covered, you being abroad and not having the mobile connection required or being in a country or timezone that is not supported, or if you provide us with the wrong mobile phone number - as per our terms.\r\n<blockquote>"When we confirm your text message reminder credit payment" means the sending of an email by Reemindme.com that your payment has been processed. This is effective regardless of whether or not you receive, look at or open the email provided it was addressed to the email address supplied by you at the time of the order.</blockquote>\r\n[/av_textblock]\r\n\r\n[/av_three_fifth][av_one_fifth]\r\n\r\n[av_contact email=''ashurazz@gmail.com'' title=''Have any queries? Write to us!'' button=''Submit'' on_send='''' sent=''Your message has been sent!'' link=''manually,http://'' subject='''' autorespond='''' captcha='''' color='''']\r\n[av_contact_field label=''Name'' type=''text'' check=''is_empty'' options='''' multi_select='''' width=''''][/av_contact_field]\r\n[av_contact_field label=''E-Mail'' type=''text'' check=''is_email'' options='''' multi_select='''' width=''''][/av_contact_field]\r\n[av_contact_field label=''Subject'' type=''text'' check=''is_empty'' options='''' multi_select='''' width='''']